{"tid":1751493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 唔好唔生仔 要薪火相傳 贏落去","createTime":"2019-11-24T17:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T03:49:21.000Z","uid":111493,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"464e1e47d50a4c70e5c39c1e13657c170b6c5a3f","tid":1751493,"uid":111493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:27:28.000Z","msg":"好難得港人覺醒<br />\n今次選舉一定令阿爺再侵入得勁<br />\n每日150加到500都唔係無可能<br />\n我地贏但我地會老<br />\n你都見到出生率 就算我地有𥌓光<br />\n但過10年無人接都係好難去終點<br />\n我地要鬥長命見證光復香港既一日<br />\n唔止我地 更要令真香港人<br />\n傳承落去！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a55df5ac9f0e3d821657154337d077f808b6aee7","tid":1751493,"uid":303766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:28:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31bb4306598d1ded2f2e3e3ebadee24c2648a90c","tid":1751493,"uid":111493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:29:32.000Z","msg":"打到喊左"},{"pid":"b104e6e0f109fc5197eea7d3f3e97c3ed44b75d6","tid":1751493,"uid":138940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:29:53.000Z","msg":"但係依家真係驚二噁英會搞到畸胎...<br />\n知唔知第日生之前係咪可以check左先"},{"pid":"c1504c57cebf488386e03f485ba4ed046b49f470","tid":1751493,"uid":262095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T03:49:21.000Z","msg":"聽起上黎即工具既意思"}]}